node.text:
Follow 👉  @bodysmartfitness for the best mindset, nutrition and fitness tips 👉  Follow @bodysmartfitness   
 
 Double tap if you agree 😂   
   
Why do so many of us spend our lives people-pleasing and trying to be liked when the reality is, we don't like everybody ourselves!   
   
Do you know who it is important that you like? 🤔   
   
YOURSELF 🥰   
   
Self-love is a phrase that many of us struggle with. It feels unusual and wrong to 'love' oneself. 😫   
   
So how about liking oneself? 😀   
   
That's OK and feels less strange, doesn't it? ✅   
   
What can you do to ensure that you like yourself? 
 
That boring unsexy stuff that is actually sexy AF and makes all the difference in how we feel towards ourselves.   
   
😴 Prioritising sleep over that next episode on Netflix   
💧 Hydrating adequately and not living off coffee and soda   
🍎 Eating a diet full of nutrients (but also allowing for what you fancy)   
🥾 Getting in your daily steps   
🧠 Looking after your mental fitness and resilience   
🏋️‍♀️ Training your body   
   
So stop trying to be liked by everybody and focus on liking yourself.   
   
@bodysmartfitness knows that is easier said than done but if you're looking to invest in the LAST thing you'll need to instil the right behaviour changes, thoughts and beliefs that will ensure your success with your health and well-being, get in touch.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MINDSET THERAPY 03 THE MAN FELT VERY SORRY AND SAID NO. HE EXPLAINED THAT HE DID NOT EVEN HAVE ENOUGH MONEY TO FIX THE STRAP OF HIS WATCH HE HAD JUST BROKEN. @mindset.therapy'.
Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MINDSET HERAPY 04 SHE DID NOT INSIST ON HER REQUEST @mindset.therapy'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MINDSET A THERAPY 05 THE MAN WENT TO WORK AND PASSED BY A WATCH SHOP SOLD HIS DAMAGED WATCH AT A LOW PRICE AND WENT TO BUY A COMB FOR HIS WIFE. @mindset.therapy'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MINDSET HERAPY 06 He CAME HOME IN THE EVENING WITH THE COMB IN HIS HAND READY TO GIVE TO HIS WIFE. @mindset.therapy'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MINDSET THERAP 07 HE WAS SURPRISED WHEN HE SAW HIS WIFE WITH A SHORT HAIRCUT. SHE HAD SOLD HER HAIR AND WAS HOLDING A NEW WATCH BAND. @mindset.therapy'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MS HERAPY 08 TEARS FLOWED SIMULTANEOUSLY FROM THEIR EYES, NOT FOR THE FUTILITY OF THEIR ACTIONS BUT FOR THE RECIPROCITY OF THEIR LOVE. @mindset.therapy'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'ANS THERAPY MINDSET 09 MORAL OF THE STORY: TO LOVE IS NOTHING TO BE LOVED IS SOMETHING. BUT TO LOVE AND TO BE LOVED BY THE ONE YOU LOVE, THAT IS EVERYTHING. @mindset.therapy'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Believe in your heart and soul that you are capable of big things in your life. The only thing that is standing in your way is yourself. Remove your glass ceiling. Type YES if you agree. MINDSET THERAPY'.

Photo by MINDSET THERAPY™ on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'This year, I've learned 3 things: 1) You're not always going to get the closure or the explanation you deserve. 2) Sometimes you have to accept something for what it is and move on. 3) Everything really does happen fora a for reason MINDSET ATHERAPY'.
